    "body": "Problem:\r\nThe exrc file in the current directory is executed twice, in `_defaults.lua` and in\r\n`do_exrc_initalization()`.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nStart search from parent directory of cwd.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nProblem:\r\n\r\nNo way to stop the search of 'exrc' files in parent directories like `|editorconfig.root|`.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nUsers can unset 'exrc' in an exrc file to stop the search.\r\n\r\nFixes bug from #34079 and solves the concern raised in a comment on that issue.\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2025-05-20T17:06:08Z",
